Thence, N 35° 14′ W, a distance of 14.47 meters to point 1;

the point of beginning, containing an area of 24, 099 square meters, more of less. Points 1 to 24 referred to are indicated in the attached plan.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF, I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

Done in the City of Manila, this 29th day of June, in the year of Our Lord, Nineteen Hundred and Seventy.

(SGD.) FERDINAND E. MARCOS President Republic of the Philippines

By the President:

(SGD.) PONCIANO G.A. MATHAY Acting Executive Secretary

